trans-unit.source: Provides a base implementation of a channel object that exposes a dictionary interface to its properties.
trans-unit.target: Gir en base implementering av et objekt for kanalen som viser et grensesnitt for ordliste til egenskapene.

trans-unit.source: BaseChannelObjectWithProperties is the base class for <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties> and <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties>.
trans-unit.target: BaseChannelObjectWithProperties er basisklasse for <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties>og <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties>.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties> </xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties>

trans-unit.source: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties> and <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties> can be used as the base classes for channels and channel sinks that provide named properties.
trans-unit.target: <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties>og <xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties>kan brukes som basisklasser for kanaler og kanal mottakere som gir navngitte egenskaper.</xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelSinkWithProperties></xref:System.Runtime.Remoting.Channels.BaseChannelWithProperties>

trans-unit.source: BaseChannelObjectWithProperties handles the complex task of asking a channel object for its properties.
trans-unit.target: BaseChannelObjectWithProperties håndterer komplekse oppgaven å stille et kanal-objekt for køens egenskaper.
